 idea is one gets better and quicker results aiming not at the actors but at the scriptwriters to help supply the themes and words for the scripts—to try to influence the areas where policy ideas percolate from academia and think tanks ideas then are the capital goods that go into building policy as a finished product—and there are insufficient libertarian capital goods at the top of the structure of production to build the policies libertarians demand   charles g koch summer fellow program institute for humane studies at george mason university retrieved  the charles g koch summer fellow program combines a paid public policy internship with two career skills seminars and weekly policy lectures you’ll gain realworld experience take a crash course in marketbased policy analysis and hone your professional skills the intensive tenweek program begins in june and includes a  stipend and a housing allowance   a b about charles g koch charles g koch foundation february    bill of rights institute media matters for america   youth entrepreneurs kansas charles g koch foundation   best donors accessed   charles koch arena wichita state university retrieved  may    wenzl roy december   koch gives  million to wichita state the wichita eagle retrieved april     suellentrop paul april   wichita state community work together to keep gregg marshall the wichita eagle retrieved april     winner of the  william e simon prize philanthropyroundtableorg    william e simon prize philanthropy roundtable philanthropy roundtable retrieved  april    nelson colleen mccain fields gary jul   obama koch brothers in unlikely alliance to overhaul criminal justice wall street journal   a b c horwitz sari aug   unlikely allies washington post   hudetz mary oct   forfeiture reform aligns likes of billionaire charles koch aclu the topeka capital journal   koch brothers join obama in advocating us prison reform russian today jul     koch charles g february   charles koch this is the one issue where bernie sanders is right the washington post retrieved february     about charles g koch charles g koch charitable foundation retrieved  december    donor aims to lick illness that he has battled for  years the chronicle of philanthropy retrieved  october    robinson peter april   good profit part i uncomomn knowledge hoover institution video interview recorded march     levinthal dave spreading the freemarket gospel the atlantic retrieved    honorary degree recipients and degrees conferred honoris causa pdf washburn   ball molly mar   do the koch brothers really care about criminaljustice reform the atlantic   may  execrank top ceos  external linksedit profile at koch industries charles g koch charitable foundation profile at philanthropy roundtable names in the news david and charles koch at followthemoneyorg political contributions from influence explorer at the sunlight foundation charles koch at bloomberg lp robinson peter april   good profit part ii uncommon knowledge hoover institution video interview recorded march    charles g koch at goodreads v t e koch family parents fred c koch – children frederick r koch  charles koch  david koch  william koch  other harry koch – major companies koch industries other organizations koch family foundations charles koch institute citizens for a sound economy americans for prosperity david h koch institute for integrative cancer research bill of rights institute cato institute see also political activities of the koch brothers mary r koch ship the science of success book mercatus center charles koch arena david h koch theater v t e koch industries invista antron comforel coolmax cordura dacron lycra polarguard solarmax stainmaster tactel thermolite georgiapacific angel soft brawny colhogar delica demakup densarmor plus dixie kittensoft lotus mardi gras moltonel okay plytanium quilted northern soft n gentle sparkle tenderly toughrock tutto vanity fair zee other units abko properties flint hills resources koch chemical technology